# Sun City Summerlin Homes — local overrides

Global rules live in **`%USERPROFILE%\.cursor\rules\`**. This file only
records **paths and versions for this repo** so agents do not guess wrong.

## Runtime & install

- **Node:** `>=22.0.0 <23` (`package.json` `engines`, **`.nvmrc`**, CI/Vercel 22.x).
- **`.npmrc`:** `engine-strict=true` — use Node 22 locally or installs fail by design.

## TypeScript

- **`@/*`** maps to repo **root** (no `src/` folder): e.g. `@/lib/site-contact`.
- **`declare module '*.css'`** in `types.d.ts` — required for TS 6+ + side-effect CSS in `app/layout.tsx`.
- Web component JSX: **`realscout-jsx.d.ts`**.

## RealScout (this site)

- **Config:** `lib/realscout-config.ts` — `realScoutAgentEncodedId`, `realScoutHomeSearchUrl` (`NEXT_PUBLIC_REALSCOUT_*`).
- **Portal link component:** `components/RealScoutHomeSearchLink.tsx` — never link buyers to **`/onboarding`**.
- **Script:** single `next/script` in `app/layout.tsx` → `realscout-web-components.umd.js` with **`type="module"`**.
- **Widgets:** `migration/pages-source/index.tsx`, `properties/index.tsx`, `search/index.tsx` (`realscout-advanced-search`).

## IDX

- Do not edit **`components/idx/**`** without explicit approval (MLS compliance).
